{
    "text": "Porto's breathtaking views will leave you in awe by @carlopes27 !\ud83d\ude0d\ud83c\udf1f  \ud83d\udca1 Porto is a coastal city in northwest Portugal known for its stately bridges and port wine production. In the medieval Ribeira (riverside) district, narrow cobbled streets wind past merchants' houses and cafes. S\u00e3o Francisco Church is known for its lavish baroque interior with ornate gilded carvings. The palatial 19th-century Pal\u00e1cio de Bolsa, formerly a stock market, was built to impress potential European investors.  Share this with someone you'd like to visit Porto with!\ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\uddf9   \ud83d\udcf8 @carlopes27 \ud83d\udccdPorto, Portugal.",
